- We did **not** fork `vercel-labs/agent-browser`. Subprocess invocation only.
- We did **not** fork `browser-use/browser-harness`. From-scratch Python implementation, design inspiration only.

If you spot any source code in this repository that appears to originate from
either project and is not properly attributed, please open an issue — we will
